{"tid":216674,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"生暗瘡生到我想自殺","createTime":"2017-04-25T10:55:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T11:08:23.000Z","uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"f407d11c799992bcf7ad410546489e9e07c65ebb","tid":216674,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"以前有女埋身 依家有結界無女行近我十米<br />\n呢排越生越勁 細過老母又唔比錢睇醫生<br />\n<br />\n 搞到成臉無一個位光滑 點做好 以下類似<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2DB1f1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2DB1f1Q.jpg&h=2bb121b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iZ6Fwu9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiZ6Fwu9.jpg&h=b52a8583&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲要嘴下個位有白頭瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5611b40a114aeb7dcf675bb0fadae14e50a7ee2","tid":216674,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:00:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43a06fc018d0005b7f37b19ac766dcd2be1d7e2d","tid":216674,"uid":46566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:02:44.000Z","msg":"a酸"},{"pid":"b2b461ac16a5e465820a35517cb87f5f210030be","tid":216674,"uid":100451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:03:22.000Z","msg":"樓主你依家幾歲？"},{"pid":"616f8ece098d4ac5aba5961c3ad770be7aa913da","tid":216674,"uid":107571,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:04:51.000Z","msg":"用暗瘡膏 此post已完"},{"pid":"d7358a324482b5700fe8f95c46575c709cd6dc87","tid":216674,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T11:06:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主你依家幾歲？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n21<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff0694ef1439672765047d0844ef16f78af9355","t