<blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係9分鐘就fail個d 想培養運動習慣 但唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實開始到第一日 堅持幾日你就會發現你習慣左<br />\n我未開始前都覺得運動 出汗係好辛苦既事,<br />\n日日想番係屋企打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪嫁，我都完全跑唔到，有冇第二啲運動推介，我就黎唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己就冇玩開運動,咩足球籃球完全唔識打 所以簡左跑步呢樣最簡單既野黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起初都覺得辛苦架 唔聽住歌我係跑唔到 中間又試過去gym room跑步機跑,一路跑一路煲劇/睇動畫 睇一集/兩集就跑完 會覺得時間過得好快<br />\n又試過不斷跑街發掘D新地方 跑到唔知去左邊<br />\n用nike app記錄低<br />\n總之就係不停搵D野令跑步變得有趣D"},{"pid":"cf7592fa4a023438dffce1226099fb9e74e7d5e9","tid":216674,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:51:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係9分鐘就fail個d 想培養運動習慣 但唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實開始到第一日 堅持幾日你就會發現你習慣左<br />\n我未開始前都覺得運動 出汗係好辛苦既事,<br />\n日日想番係屋企打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪嫁，我都完全跑唔到，有冇第二啲運動推介，我就黎唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都係唔鐘意岀街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a953136cde64bb02376f182b34cf26887f2ca876","tid":216674,"uid":12823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:52:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都係9分鐘就fail個d 想培養運動習慣 但唔知點入手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己太懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實開始到第一日 堅持幾日你就會發現你習慣左<br />\n我未開始前都覺得運動 出汗係好辛苦既事,<br />\n日日想番係屋企打機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n係咪嫁，我都完全跑唔到，有冇第二啲運動推介，我就黎唔想出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我自己就冇玩開運動,咩足球籃球完全唔識打 所以簡左跑步呢樣最簡單既野黎做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n起初都覺得辛苦架 唔聽住歌我係跑唔到 中間又試過去gym room跑步機跑,一路跑一路煲劇/睇動畫 睇一集/兩集就跑完 會覺得時間過得好快<br />\n又試過不斷跑街發掘D新地方 跑到唔知去左邊<br />\n用nike app記錄低<br />\n總之就係不停搵D野令跑步變得有趣D</blockquote><br />\n我之前跑個陣成日會右下腹痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da0e179ca06890105941d0f5d149da9b25acfc7","tid":216674,"uid":47109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:02:00.000Z","msg":"其實你地係塊面冇得救之前到底做左咩<br />\n我以前爛面果陣隔日跑步 戒甜戒凍 11點訓6點醒 刺激性重口味嘅野都戒埋<br />\n冇食藥 搽吓普通護膚品咁<br />\nkeep左半年都好番晒 <br />\n如果你地個生活習慣唔變淨係想靠食藥/搽野好就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只能夠講祝你早日好番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a32e1edbd7e32ae31bdb85cdeae64ad63384542","tid":216674,"uid":47109,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:03:47.000Z","msg":"呢樣唔得果樣唔慣就唔好搞咁多野<br />\n接受佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你估變靚好睇唔洗付出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"372bc5304e89fedd00bb4d8f36feaf3f08706aaa","tid":216674,"uid":2002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T08:35:38.000Z","msg":"有做gym都會生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cf8414544c842c84b1d714cdadb86ec991fd135","tid":216674,"uid":51250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T09:38:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>上面巴打係本身無運重習慣？ 一開波點適應？</blockquote><br />\n其實係頭兩三日辛苦